{"tid":1085788,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"狼猴熊豬狗大集合！2019日本同志先生今決選","createTime":"2019-03-31T11:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T14:18:35.000Z","uid":121473,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"98df5502a3914f34efbd62962e1cb2b70e56292a","tid":1085788,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T11:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PuOWnFn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPuOWnFn.png&h=1c46a42d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T1xW67K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT1xW67K.jpg&h=997f7a86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翻攝《Instagram》mrgayjapan<br />\n<br />\n2019日本同志先生（MR GAY JAPAN 2019）就在今天（31日）要進行決選啦！官網上公布了5位決選名單，真是環肥燕瘦、熊豬猴狗狼，各種特色都有，讓人眼花撩亂！<br />\n <br />\n《Instagram》mrgayjapan上，也分享了好多他們的生活照與幕後照，每1位都看起來健康又陽光，幽默且滿臉笑容，雖然面貌與身材不同，但都散發滿滿的正能量啦！<br />\n <br />\n1名在日本生活了10年的香港男子H，就在《日本集合》網站分享心得說，作為1名深櫃同志，在東京生活「不是很困難的」。<br />\n <br />\nH男說，首先的原因是：「你身邊所有日本人，都有2個面孔」，而回頭看看自己，「就不會覺得自己活得很虛偽」。<br />\n <br />\n第2個原因則是，「在日本，同志的多樣性，其實是多的」，「他們接受不同的人，不同的身形」，因此，不同身材長相的參賽者都有，也都被接納，甚至獲選前5名。所以，不管是長成怎樣的同志，都不會被單一的外貌與身材標準所限制，可以活得自由開心。<br />\n <br />\nH男還說，第3個原因是，東京的同志圈很珍惜朋友，不忍心互相傷害。因為許多人都是離鄉背井、辛苦地生活著，他們重視、在乎朋友，認為朋友與家人一樣重要，「大家都想幸福，大家都想快樂，大家都被歧視，所以大家在可以的時候，都不需要再傷害大家」。<br />\n <br />\n根據日本同志先生網站消息，獲選冠軍的日本同志先生，將在4/28-5/4到南非開普敦，參加2019年世界同志先生大賽！一起來看看，到底誰會獲選呢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190331/1542750/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190331%2F1542750%2F&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP9yJMs%2BH1ZGqELk%2BE%2F7wpkaY%3D&h=cfadaa64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190331%2F1542750%2F&h=15f27e8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190331/1542750/</a>"},{"pid":"477dd29f89b9daa9e560934fecc859f8d9735550","tid":1085788,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T13:02:12.000Z","msg":"AKIRA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d5c0239a8a2402fd6a7fa71ae0a416e6004a2e","tid":1085788,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T13:06:25.000Z","msg":"非Gay<br />\n上面嗰班無真崎航同佢班仔咁正"},{"pid":"45251e2d523a4d20bd84b273fc791d62bdd9dbf6","tid":1085788,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T13:10:45.000Z","msg":"tiger <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鍾意眼大大"},{"pid":"06be85da65e5d56e535ceb96f7939fffcaa22670","tid":1085788,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T14:18:35.000Z","msg":"IG<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/mrgayjapan/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmrgayjapan%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP9yJMs%2BH1ZGqELk%2BE%2F7wpkaY%3D&h=79eb8b1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/mrgayjapan/?utm_source=ig_embed</a>"}]}